00:29:59.957 --> 00:30:01.040
KIM KARDASHIAN WEST: Yeah.

00:30:01.040 --> 00:30:05.480
So Chris Young has been in
prison for almost nine years.

00:30:05.480 --> 00:30:07.640
And he is 30 years old.

00:30:07.640 --> 00:30:12.470
He made bad choices--

00:30:12.470 --> 00:30:16.080
low-level drug offender.

00:30:16.080 --> 00:30:18.260
He had marijuana.

00:30:18.260 --> 00:30:22.610
On the floor of his car, he
had, like, crumbs of cocaine.

00:30:22.610 --> 00:30:24.590
And so they couldn't
even measure it,

00:30:24.590 --> 00:30:26.430
so they just said
it was half a gram.

00:30:26.430 --> 00:30:29.660
And he had two previous
really low-level charges,

00:30:29.660 --> 00:30:33.780
like the one that
he was charged with.

00:30:33.780 --> 00:30:36.140
And so they gave him life.

00:30:36.140 --> 00:30:39.280
And he has sickle cell anemia.

00:30:39.280 --> 00:30:40.820
He's been in and
out of hospitals--

00:30:40.820 --> 00:30:42.350
two hip replacements.

00:30:45.000 --> 00:30:48.480
And even just what Alice said--

00:30:48.480 --> 00:30:51.570
Chris has the same
sentence as Charles Manson.

00:30:51.570 --> 00:30:56.740
That just, to me,
sounds so insane.

00:30:56.740 --> 00:31:03.340
So anyone that I
can bring light to,

00:31:03.340 --> 00:31:07.330
just to share how
he's in-- because

00:31:07.330 --> 00:31:11.660
