judge has resigned.

00:31:13.886 --> 00:31:15.760
And the judge came with
me to the White House

00:31:15.760 --> 00:31:20.400
to talk to the president
about how he could not

00:31:20.400 --> 00:31:25.040
live with himself having
to sentence these young men

00:31:25.040 --> 00:31:30.357
and women for life over
really low-level drug crimes.

00:31:30.357 --> 00:31:31.690
MALIKA SAADA SAAR: That's right.

00:31:31.690 --> 00:31:32.490
That's right.

00:31:32.490 --> 00:31:36.600
Ms. Alice, you are free now.

00:31:36.600 --> 00:31:39.420
And it's only been
four months, right?

00:31:39.420 --> 00:31:40.380
ALICE JOHNSON: Yes.

00:31:40.380 --> 00:31:42.120
MALIKA SAADA SAAR:
