00:33:46.150 --> 00:33:47.620
Come and talk to me.

00:33:47.620 --> 00:33:53.140
So for me, I've seen that
that has become a reality.

00:33:53.140 --> 00:33:58.120
And like I mentioned earlier,
I don't think the people inside

00:33:58.120 --> 00:33:59.600
want to wait those years.

00:33:59.600 --> 00:34:00.350
ALICE JOHNSON: No.

00:34:00.350 --> 00:34:01.849
KIM KARDASHIAN WEST:
So I just would

00:34:01.849 --> 00:34:03.760
urge people to talk
to the president,

00:34:03.760 --> 00:34:07.540
to talk to Jared Kushner,
to continue to speak out

00:34:07.540 --> 00:34:08.469
through social media.

00:34:08.469 --> 00:34:09.520
Share stories.

00:34:09.520 --> 00:34:11.139
If I hadn't been
on social media,

00:34:11.139 --> 00:34:12.870
I wouldn't have
seen Alice's story.

00:34:12.870 --> 00:34:17.350
So even people just
passing along stories--

00:34:17.350 --> 00:34:18.110
reach out to me.

00:34:18.110 --> 00:34:19.960
I'm not afraid to go
to the White House.

00:34:19.960 --> 00:34:20.530
Let me know.

00:34:20.530 --> 00:34:22.030
I'll take a story there.

00:34:22.030 --> 00:34:23.889
ALICE JOHNSON: I just
want to say this, too,

00:34:23.889 --> 00:34:28.360
