00:34:33.250 --> 00:34:36.489
It takes courage to act.

00:34:36.489 --> 00:34:39.639
To be an activist means
that you've got to act.

00:34:39.639 --> 00:34:41.199
You've got to do something.

00:34:41.199 --> 00:34:44.530
You just can't turn your
head, as Kim said, and wait

00:34:44.530 --> 00:34:46.200
another four years,
