It was demonized.

00:35:39.652 --> 00:35:41.860
MALIKA SAADA SAAR: Demonized
and dehumanizing, right?

00:35:41.860 --> 00:35:42.220
ALICE JOHNSON: Dehumanized.

00:35:42.220 --> 00:35:42.761
That's right.

00:35:42.761 --> 00:35:45.010
MALIKA SAADA SAAR: And we
had certain individuals,

00:35:45.010 --> 00:35:48.130
and communities,
and families seen

00:35:48.130 --> 00:35:52.580
as predators and given
sentences that were

