00:39:31.330 --> 00:39:33.250
my image was free
before I was free.

00:39:33.250 --> 00:39:33.875
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:39:33.875 --> 00:39:34.230
MALIKA SAADA SAAR: That's right.

00:39:34.230 --> 00:39:34.920
AUDIENCE: Wow.

00:39:34.920 --> 00:39:36.253
MALIKA SAADA SAAR: That's right.

00:39:36.253 --> 00:39:39.267
[APPLAUSE]

00:39:44.185 --> 00:39:46.730
So we've recognized
how Google has

00:39:46.730 --> 00:39:51.530
played a small, but important
role in your freedom.

00:39:51.530 --> 00:39:56.780
But Ms. Alice, you called
on us from behind bars.

00:39:56.780 --> 00:40:00.410
You called on us, as a
company, to take action

00:40:00.410 --> 00:40:01.762
and to take responsibility.

00:40:01.762 --> 00:40:02.170
ALICE JOHNSON: Yes.

00:40:02.170 --> 00:40:03.211
MALIKA SAADA SAAR: Right?

00:40:03.211 --> 00:40:07.850
And you said to us, to whom
much is given, much is required.

00:40:07.850 --> 00:40:11.630
And Kim, you are living
out that notion of to whom

00:40:11.630 --> 00:40:14.900
much is given, much is
required in your activism

00:40:14.900 --> 00:40:17.010
for justice reform.

00:40:17.010 --> 00:40:22.220
I want to know from
both of you, what more

00:40:22.220 --> 00:40:26.600
can tech do around the
issue of justice reform?

00:40:29.140 --> 00:40:32.200
KIM KARDASHIAN WEST: Just
seeing videos like that

00:40:32.200 --> 00:40:35.140
and putting it out
there on social media--

00:40:35.140 --> 00:40:36.790
I mean, I do get
how social media

00:40:36.790 --> 00:40:40.030
can be very mentally
challenging at times

00:40:40.030 --> 00:40:42.320
when you see a
lot of negativity.

00:40:42.320 --> 00:40:45.340
But if I were to take
in all the negativity

00:40:45.340 --> 00:40:50.050
that I've received over
the decade of me being

00:40:50.050 --> 00:40:55.480
in the business to that moment
where I saw Alice's video,

00:40:55.480 --> 00:40:56.990
it's all worth it.

00:40:56.990 --> 00:40:59.755
So I think, you know, it's true.

00:40:59.755 --> 00:41:01.060
[APPLAUSE]

00:41:01.930 --> 00:41:04.540
I think social
media's very powerful.

00:41:04.540 --> 00:41:06.070
And it's just like anything.

00:41:06.070 --> 00:41:10.310
If you take it in doses and if
you use it in the right way--

00:41:10.310 --> 00:41:13.420
I've been able to connect
with so many people

00:41:13.420 --> 00:41:14.680
over social media.

00:41:14.680 --> 00:41:17.960
And I'm so grateful for it.

00:41:17.960 --> 00:41:23.550
So I think if people could
just share more and share

00:41:23.550 --> 00:41:26.070
their stories more--
even seeing in the video

00:41:26.070 --> 00:41:28.950
that you guys posted of
the love letters, I think,

00:41:28.950 --> 00:41:32.220
that John Legend
was sharing, was so

00:41:32.220 --> 00:41:36.450
touching because so many
people are affected by it,

00:41:36.450 --> 00:41:38.610
people that you
wouldn't even imagine.

00:41:38.610 --> 00:41:39.651
MALIKA SAADA SAAR: Mm-hm.

00:41:39.651 --> 00:41:41.280
That's so True.

00:41:41.280 --> 00:41:44.940
ALICE JOHNSON: I don't think
Googlers who are here today

00:41:44.940 --> 00:41:47.790
really realize the role
that this company played

00:41:47.790 --> 00:41:48.470
in my freedom.

00:41:48.470 --> 00:41:49.740
Are they aware of the
role that they played?

00:41:49.740 --> 00:41:51.490
MALIKA SAADA SAAR: You
talk more about it.

00:41:51.490 --> 00:41:52.266
ALICE JOHNSON: OK.

00:41:52.266 --> 00:41:53.664
[LAUGHTER]

00:41:54.600 --> 00:41:58.910
The Google event that I spoke
at that was Skyped out--

00:41:58.910 --> 00:42:01.680
a person who was sitting
in the audience saw me.

00:42:01.680 --> 00:42:02.880
MALIKA SAADA SAAR: I have to
say we did it on a YouTube

00:42:02.880 --> 00:42:04.629
platform, because I'll
get in trouble if I

00:42:04.629 --> 00:42:05.892
allow you to say "Skype."

00:42:05.892 --> 00:42:06.384
ALICE JOHNSON: OK.

00:42:06.384 --> 00:42:06.884
OK.

00:42:06.884 --> 00:42:10.320
[LAUGHTER]

00:42:10.320 --> 00:42:12.668
Anyway, I just want you
to know that Google--

00:42:12.668 --> 00:42:14.340
[LAUGHTER]

00:42:14.340 --> 00:42:17.970
I just want you to know
that Google did play a role

00:42:17.970 --> 00:42:20.550
as a catalyst for my freedom.

00:42:20.550 --> 00:42:22.130
So thank you.

00:42:22.130 --> 00:42:23.490
You've welcomed me here today.

00:42:23.490 --> 00:42:26.940
But I want to tell you,
Google, I love you, Google.

00:42:26.940 --> 00:42:29.040
I love you, Googlers.

00:42:29.040 --> 00:42:31.650
I think it's OK to say that.

00:42:31.650 --> 00:42:35.150
[APPLAUSE]

00:42:36.270 --> 00:42:38.520
Without telling the
whole story, just

00:42:38.520 --> 00:42:40.170
know that you were a catalyst.

00:42:40.170 --> 00:42:43.050
You played a role in my freedom.

00:42:43.050 --> 00:42:44.640
And today, I was
able to meet some

00:42:44.640 --> 00:42:47.640
of the behind-the-scene people
at Google who played a role

00:42:47.640 --> 00:42:48.790
and give them a hug.

00:42:48.790 --> 00:42:53.130
And I want to give all
of you a virtual hug now.

00:42:53.130 --> 00:42:55.170
Those who I have
not seen, some--

00:42:55.170 --> 00:42:57.690
I know this has
been live-streamed--

00:42:57.690 --> 00:43:00.540
I'm very grateful to the
role that Google played

00:43:00.540 --> 00:43:04.050
in my being a free woman today.

00:43:04.050 --> 00:43:07.080
And technology is so-- to
get back to what you said--

00:43:07.080 --> 00:43:10.110
technology-- had that
technology been in place--

00:43:10.110 --> 00:43:11.790
it was my timing.

00:43:11.790 --> 00:43:13.710
It was the exact time.

00:43:13.710 --> 00:43:17.290
When I went into prison,
there was no social media.

00:43:17.290 --> 00:43:18.430
There was no Facebook.

00:43:18.430 --> 00:43:20.620
There was no internet.

00:43:20.620 --> 00:43:24.060
So my understanding
now of just how big

00:43:24.060 --> 00:43:26.940
this is, to have all
of these followers--

00:43:26.940 --> 00:43:29.231
I have some
followers myself now.

00:43:29.231 --> 00:43:31.155
[LAUGHTER]

00:43:31.155 --> 00:43:34.522
[CHEERING AND APPLAUSE]

00:43:36.940 --> 00:43:39.190
To understand how this works--

00:43:39.190 --> 00:43:41.740
and one follower can have--

00:43:41.740 --> 00:43:44.910
just one follower can
have a lot of followers,

00:43:44.910 --> 00:43:49.820
who have a lot of followers,
who can get this message out.

00:43:49.820 --> 00:43:53.110
So technology
plays a huge role--

00:43:53.110 --> 00:43:55.880
now that I know something
about technology--

00:43:55.880 --> 00:44:00.010
it plays a huge role in
getting the message out.

00:44:00.010 --> 00:44:02.250
It played a role in my freedom.

00:44:02.250 --> 00:44:05.530
And it's going to play,
it is going to play,

00:44:05.530 --> 00:44:07.393
a big role in the
freedom of others.

00:44:07.393 --> 00:44:08.059
AUDIENCE: Right.

00:44:08.059 --> 00:44:08.548
ALICE JOHNSON: Right.

00:44:08.548 --> 00:44:09.214
AUDIENCE: Right.

00:44:09.214 --> 00:44:11.971
[APPLAUSE]

