00:44:29.850 --> 00:44:32.970
It's always so amazing
to get to see her family.

00:44:32.970 --> 00:44:37.530
And that's what we're fighting
for-- is for more people

00:44:37.530 --> 00:44:40.950
to get the opportunities
to see, and touch, and be

00:44:40.950 --> 00:44:42.436
with their loved ones again.

00:44:42.436 --> 00:44:43.311
ALICE JOHNSON: Mm-hm.

00:44:43.311 --> 00:44:43.810
Absolutely.

00:44:43.810 --> 00:44:46.320
ALICE JOHNSON: My parting
words to the audience

00:44:46.320 --> 00:44:51.360
here is that one person
can make a difference.

00:44:51.360 --> 00:44:53.386
That one person could be you.

00:44:53.386 --> 00:44:54.378
AUDIENCE: Yes.

00:44:54.378 --> 00:44:55.866
MALIKA SAADA SAAR: Thank you.

00:44:55.866 --> 00:44:57.354
Thank you.

00:44:57.354 --> 00:45:00.826
[APPLAUSE]

